\c 35
\s Umthetho wesabatha
\p
\v 1 UMozisi wasebuthanisa inhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli, wathi kubo: La ngamazwi iN\nd kosi\nd* ewalayileyo ukuthi \add li\add*wenze\x + 34.32.\x*.
\v 2 Insuku eziyisithupha kuzakwenziwa umsebenzi\x + 20.9.\x*, kodwa ngosuku lwesikhombisa kuzakuba yibungcwele kini, isabatha lokuphumula eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; loba ngubani owenza umsebenzi ngalo uzabulawa.
\v 3 Lingabasi umlilo ngosuku lwesabatha kuyo yonke imizi yenu\x + 16.23.\x*.
\s Ukunikela umnikelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni
\p
\v 4 UMozisi wasekhuluma kunhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli esithi: Yile into iN\nd kosi\nd* eyilayileyo isithi\x + 25.9. 25.1-7.\x*:
\v 5 Thathani phakathi kwenu umnikelo ube ngoweN\nd kosi\nd*; loba ngubani olenhliziyo evumayo kawulethe, umnikelo weN\nd kosi\nd*, igolide lesiliva lethusi,
\v 6 lokuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka lokuyibubende lokubomvu, lelembu elicolekileyo kakhulu, loboya bembuzi,
\v 7 lezikhumba eziphendulwe zababomvu zezinqama, lezikhumba zikamantswane, lezihlahla zesinga,
\v 8 lamafutha ezibane, lamakha amafutha okugcoba lempepha elephunga elimnandi,
\v 9 lamatshe \w ama-onikse\w**, lamatshe okubekwa awe-efodi lawesembatho sesifuba.
\v 10 Labo bonke abalenhliziyo ehlakaniphileyo phakathi kwenu\x + 28.3.\x* kabeze benze konke iN\nd kosi\nd* ekulayileyo;
\v 11 ithabhanekele\x + 26.1-30\x*, ithente lalo, lesifulelo salo, ingwegwe zalo, lamapulanka alo, imithando yalo, insika zalo, lezisekelo zalo;
\v 12 umtshokotsho, lemijabo yawo, isihlalo somusa\x + 25.10-16.\x*, leveyili lesembeso\x + 26.31,33. 39.34. 40.3,21. Nani 4.5.\x*;
\v 13 itafula, lemijabo yalo, lezitsha zalo zonke\x + 25.23-29.\x*, lezinkwa zokubukiswa\x + 25.30.\x*;
\v 14 loluthi lwesibane sesikhanyiso, lezitsha zalo, lezibane zalo\x + 25.31-39.\x*, lamafutha esikhanyiso\x + 27.20.\x*;
\v 15 lelathi lempepha, lemijabo yalo\x + 30.1-10.\x*, lamafutha okugcoba\x + 30.23-33.\x*, lempepha elephunga elimnandi\x + 30.34-38.\x*, lesilenge somnyango emnyango wethabhanekele\x + 26.36\x*;
\v 16 ilathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa\x + 27.1-8.\x*, lesihlengo sethusi elilaso, imijabo yalo, lazo zonke izitsha zalo, inditshi yokugezela lonyawo lwayo\x + 30.18-21.\x*;
\v 17 amakhetheni eguma, insika zalo, lezisekelo zazo, lesilenge sesango leguma\x + 27.9-17.\x*;
\v 18 izikhonkwane zethabhanekele, lezikhonkwane zeguma\x + 27.19.\x*, lentambo zazo\x + 39.40.\x*;
\v 19 izembatho ezifekethisiweyo zokukhonza endaweni engcwele, izembatho ezingcwele zikaAroni umpristi\x + 31.10. 39.1,41.\x*, lezembatho zamadodana akhe, ukusebenza njengabapristi.
\s Abantu banikela umnikelo wabo
\p
\v 20 Lenhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli yaphuma phambi kukaMozisi.
\v 21 Beza-ke, wonke onhliziyo yakhe eyamvusayo\x + 35.26. 36.2. 25.2. 35.5,22,29.\x*, laye wonke omoya wakhe owamenza wavuma, baletha umnikelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni emsebenzini wethente lenhlangano lowenkonzo yonke yalo lowezembatho ezingcwele.
\v 22 Beza-ke abesilisa kanye labesifazana, bonke abavumayo ngenhliziyo, baletha iziceco\x + 2 Kho. 19.28. Isa. 37.29. Hez. 19.4,9; 29.4.\x* lamacici\x + Gen. 24.22.\x* lendandatho lamasongo\x + Nani 31.50.\x*, zonke izinto zegolide; laye wonke owazunguza umnikelo wokuzunguzwa wegolide eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 23 Laye wonke okwatholakala kuye\x + 35.24. 1 Lan. 29.8.\x* okuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka lokuyibubende lokubomvu\x + 25.4,5. 35.6,7.\x* lelembu elicolekileyo kakhulu loboya bembuzi lezikhumba eziphendulwe zababomvu zenqama lezikhumba zikamantswane bakuletha.
\v 24 Wonke owanikela umnikelo wokuzunguzwa wesiliva lowethusi bakuletha kungumnikelo wokuzunguzwa weN\nd kosi\nd*; laye wonke okwatholakala kuye izihlahla zesinga ezawo wonke umsebenzi wenkonzo baziletha.
\v 25 Labo bonke abesifazana ababehlakaniphile\x + 28.3.\x* ngenhliziyo baphotha ngezandla zabo, baletha okuphothiweyo\x + 2 Kho. 23.7. Zaga 31.19,22,24.\x*, okuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka, lokuyibubende, okubomvu, lelembu elicolekileyo kakhulu.
\v 26 Labo bonke abesifazana abanhliziyo zabo zabavusa\x + 35.21.\x* enhlakanipheni baphotha uboya bembuzi\x + 2 Kho. 23.7. Zaga 31.19,22,24.\x*.
\v 27 Lezinduna zaletha\x + 1 Lan. 29.6. Ezra 2.68.\x* amatshe \w ama-onikse\w**\x + Gen. 2.12.\x* lamatshe okubekwa, awe-efodi lawesembatho sesifuba,
\v 28 la\x + 30.23.\x*makha\x + 35.8.\x* lamafutha awesibane, lawamafutha okugcoba, lawempepha elephunga elimnandi.
\v 29 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli bawuletha umnikelo wesihle eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 35.21. 36.3. 1 Lan. 29.9.\x*. Bonke abesilisa labesifazana abanhliziyo zabo zabenza bavuma ukulethela wonke umsebenzi iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayiwulayile ukuthi wenziwe ngesandla sikaMozisi.
\s Ukubizwa kukaBhezaleli loOholiyaba
\p
\v 30 UMozisi wasesithi ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli: Bonani, iN\nd kosi\nd* imbizile ngebizo uBhezaleli indodana kaUri, indodana kaHuri owesizwe sakoJuda\x + 35.34; 31.2-6.\x*;
\v 31 imgcwalisile ngoMoya kaNkulunkulu enhlakanipheni, ekuqedisiseni, lelwazini, lemisebenzini yobungcitshi yonke,
\v 32 lokuthi acebe ubungcitshi ukusebenza ngegolide langesiliva langethusi,
\v 33 lekubazeni amatshe okufakwa, lekubazeni izigodo, ukusebenza emisebenzini yonke yeminwe ngobungcitshi.
\v 34 Ifakile laye enhliziyweni yakhe ukufundisa, yena loOholiyaba indodana kaAhisamaki owesizwe sakoDani.
\v 35 Ibagcwalisile ngokuhlakanipha kwenhliziyo\x + 35.31; 31.3,6. 1 Kho. 7.14. 2 Lan. 2.14.\x*, ukwenza wonke umsebenzi wombazi, lowengcitshi, lowomfekethisi ngenalithi\x + 26.36.\x*, ngokuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka langokuyibubende, ngokubomvu langelembu elicolekileyo kakhulu, lowomeluki\x + 28.32.\x*; besenza wonke umsebenzi beceba ubungcitshi.